\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：你又遲到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 返9:30以家11:00<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：又點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我遲到上午一半工作量=長工全日<br />\n仲要我幫佢地手再超額完成<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：聽日唔想見到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n（倉長揀選返個返）<br />\n第二日倉長叫我返<br />\n見到腦細對住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n??</blockquote><br />\n做得倉務既人係咁上下架啦"},{"pid":"c9258acd0234d7ee303f57c48afaf1e0145e9a39","tid":433645,"uid":50610,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T06:09:28.000Z","msg":"落地盤做保養之類嘅工<br />\n有次落地盤，出面成35度，做左兩個鐘頭野成身汗，想話入番自己公司貨櫃飲啖水，見到貨櫃入面老細坐係到講緊電話，另外有個同事做緊文件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，跟住行緊去自己位拎水時，老細收左線叫我做咩入黎，仲唔出番去做野？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我興到想斬人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 跟住拎左水之後，臨離開貨櫃一野丟左頂安全帽砰落貨櫃牆上，再砰門，聽同事講嚇到老細彈起，仲問同事我係咪發老牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n𠴱日仲要做到晒甩皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另一單係公司要幫渠記搞open day 某啲booth <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nManger 俾得三日叫我地準備晒啲野，仲要呢三日我同另一個一齊做呢單野嘅同事病左，我地都頂硬上，咁到open day 當日我地發現有一件demo模型壞左，咁我地唔用𠴱件模型，淨係放兩件上去booth到<br />\nManger問我同事點解少左一個模型，屌鳩我地唔準備好，俾咁多日都做唔好，唔識檢查左先咩？<br />\n但件模型我地都係當日先收到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我係同事隔離，我就聽到manger 好大聲咁係電話屌我地，咁我係隔離大大聲講：屌你老母呀，俾得𠴱少少時間準備條撚呀仆街，佢係咪憨撚鳩嫁屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我同事聽到即刻係電話講喂喂想cover我把聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n結果都係俾manger聽到，佢即刻發晒癲話非常非常非常不滿意我地今日嘅表現會話俾老細聽，同埋要求我注意自己言行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n結果open day老細落黎睇，話我地講解得好好又準備足夠，仲係group到表揚我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，manger即刻轉軚附和<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n過左呢件事manger怕左我，但我做多一年就冇做了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eab86b7f02421989ebc9ab666e97686563cdf1e4","tid":433645,"uid":93194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T06:21:23.000Z","msg":"叫佢讀完 MIT 再同我講野"},{"pid":"bce67b368f6cd935a2b3a29005bde9c83279f729","tid":433645,"uid":126384,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T06:29:53.000Z","msg":"做pt call center 比人屌Hea<br />\n其實係個老女人要求高<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢當眾問我點解咁小call<br />\n我話你估我地同事係機械人？間中一兩日小call都要問問問，你比咩人工我咪交咩貨<br />\n<br />\n沒幾耐我沒做，但最後全部pt都加左$10 時薪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}